			y: 5.0d
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "After defeating the 2nd Guardian of Gaia, assuming that you consumed some water from the Well of Mimir, you'll receive a Rune Tablet of Fymbultyr which is essencially the base for every ritual added by Mythic Botany"
			dependencies: [
