			subtitle: "The Agronomical Sourcelink will produce Source from crops and trees growth. Certain plants, such as MageBlooms, Source Berry Bushes or Archwood trees will produce more Source per growing stage. After Source is produced, it will be automatically placed in any Sources Jars present in a 5x5 radius. Bonemealing crops/trees will not give any Source"
