			x: -2.5d
			y: 7.0d
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "The Vitalic Sourcelink will generate healthy amounts of Source by consuming burnable items. Archwood logs will generate more Source, with Blazing Archwood logs generating the most amount of Source. Ocasionally, the Volcanic Sourcelink will turn Stone Blocks located underneath it in a 3x3 area into Magma Blocks, and the Magma Blocks, into Lava. It can also spawn Lava Lilys untop Lava. Lava Lilys are decorative blocks"
