			subtitle: "The Vitalic Sourcelink will generate Source when mobs are killed near it. It will also generate Source when nearby animals breed. Source will also be generated passively vrom the nearby baby animals. Lastly, the Vitalic Sourcelink will accelerate the growth of the neaby baby animals"
			dependencies: ["0D4195630819F997"]
