		{
			title: "Summoning an Abomination"
			x: 3.5d
			y: 5.0d
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "When used in its regular state, the Ritual of Summoning Wilden will spawn one of the 3 Wilden Mobs added by Ars Nouveau (Wilden Hunter, Wilden Stalker, Wilden Defender). However, when it is augmented with a Wilden Spike, a Wilden Horn and a Wilden Wing, the Ritual will summon the Wilden Chimera which is a challenging and destructive boss. When summoning the Chimera, this ritual will destroy some blocks around the Brazier"
			dependencies: [
				"51C8A2EC12659993"
				"23BF297FF4BD920D"
			]
			id: "33961BEFB0C5C741"
			tasks: [{
