			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "Generates mana out of Shulkers fighting other monsters. If a shulker inflicts Levitation on a monster it targets, both the shulker and the hit entity are in the flower's range, and the flower has no mana stored in its buffer, it will kill both entities, suppress their drops, and completely fill its buffer. As shulkers do not spawn naturally and don't attack other monsters on their own, a Cocoon of Caprice can be used to spawn them, and a Heisei Dream to cause them to target monsters"
